item.description:
We'll meet at the Cushing House Garden at 11:00 am at 98 High Street - that's where you pick up tickets and start the tour.  There are 11 gardens to tour all over Newburyport and Amesbury.  Your ticket gets you in both days so if you want to go back on Sunday that works. Tickets are $25.00 and you can get them by calling 978 462-2681.  http://newburyportgardentour.com/

Looking forward to seeing you on Saturday!
item.how_to_find_us: Meet at Cushing House Garden (98 High St) at 11:00 am I'll have a sign "Old Ladies Travel" in my hands
